metadata.title: Evektor SportStar
aws::graph::propositions: Evektor SportStar Variants
EuroStar SL is a model of Evektor SportStar for the European ultralight category.
EuroStar SL has a gross weight of 1,041 lb (472 kg).
EuroStar SL+ is a version of the EuroStar SL.
EuroStar SL+ has a new wing.
EuroStar SL+ has integral fuel tanks.
EuroStar SL+ has a bigger baggage compartment.
EuroStar SL+ has a lower empty weight by 8 kg (18 lb) compared to EuroStar SL.
More than 1,000 EuroStar SL+ aircraft have been built.
EuroStar SL+ was one of the top ten ultralights sold in Germany in 2014 according to Aerokurier.
EuroStar SLW is a model of Evektor SportStar for the European ultralight category.
EuroStar SLW has a gross weight of 1,041 lb (472 kg).
EuroStar SLW combines the EuroStar fuselage with the wing and stabilizer from the Harmony.
Harmony is a model of Evektor SportStar for the US Light Sport Aircraft (LSA) market.
Harmony is based on the Harmony airframe.
Harmony has enlarged ailerons and rudder to improve crosswind capabilities.
Harmony has an improved wing.
Harmony has winglets.
Harmony has an improved tail.
Harmony has a wider cockpit.
Harmony has a longer cockpit.
Harmony has refined wheel pants.
Harmony has refined fairings.

text:
## Variants
EuroStar SL
Model for the European ultralight category, with a gross weight of 1,041 lb (472 kg)
EuroStar SL+
Version of the EuroStar SL with a new wing and integral fuel tanks, bigger baggage compartment and lower empty weight by 8 kg (18 lb). More than 1,000 have been built and it was one of the top ten ultralights sold in Germany in 2014 according to Aerokurier.
EuroStar SLW
Model for the European ultralight category, with a gross weight of 1,041 lb (472 kg). It combines the EuroStar fuselage with the wing and stabilizer from the Harmony.
Harmony
Model for the US LSA market, based on the Harmony airframe, with enlarged ailerons and rudder to improve crosswind capabilities, an improved wing, winglets and tail, wider and longer cockpit, as well as refined wheel pants and other fairings.
